00:46:01,253 --> 00:46:02,971
Yeah.

617
00:46:03,133 --> 00:46:06,045
There's a dance on Friday.
Did you know?

618
00:46:08,013 --> 00:46:09,571
Yeah.

619
00:46:10,093 --> 00:46:12,049
Wanna go?

620
00:46:13,653 --> 00:46:17,043
- Thanks. I have a date.
- Oh.

621
00:46:17,773 --> 00:46:21,004
