652
00:49:32,733 --> 00:49:34,166
LUCAS:
I'm so sorry.

653
00:49:39,093 --> 00:49:41,323
ALISE: You think I'm stupid?
You think I can't see?

654
00:49:41,493 --> 00:49:43,484
CAPPIE: I don't think that.
