655
00:49:43,653 --> 00:49:44,802
CAPPIE:
You're overreacting.

656
00:49:44,973 --> 00:49:49,171
ALISE: I turn around, and you're walking
with her or looking or smiling at her.

657
00:49:49,333 --> 00:49:51,210
